content.text:
1) Описание палитры
Выбрана холодная палитра Slate–Teal: глубокий «ink» для текста, светлый «frost» с мятным оттенком для стеклянных подложек и спокойные акценты petrol/jade. Это сочетание дает ощущение надежности, премиальности и технологичности без агрессии и усталости глаз. Тона нейтрально-холодные и не кричащие, хорошо читаются на светлом фоне и поддерживают glassmorphism. Для статусов применены сдержанные jade (success), muted amber (warning), soft violet (error) и steel-teal (info) — без красного и черного.

2) Основные цвета палитры
```
| Назначение          | HEX код  | RGB/RGBA значение              | Описание                             |
|---------------------|----------|--------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| Текст основной      | #20323B  | rgb(32, 50, 59)               | Глубокий «ink» для контраста         |
| Фон основной        | #F5FAF9  | rgba(245, 250, 249, 0.9)      | Светлый frost с прозрачностью        |
| Акцент 1            | #49B29F  | rgb(73, 178, 159)             | Кнопки/CTA, позитивные состояния     |
| Акцент 2            | #7BA5B5  | rgb(123, 165, 181)            | Ховер/фокус, вторичные акценты       |
| Границы             | #B2CCD2  | rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.6)      | Полупрозрачные стеклянные бордеры    |
| Тени                | —        | rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.25)        | Мягкие глубокие тени (teal-ink)      |
```

3) Полный CSS файл
```css
/* НОВАЯ ЦВЕТОВАЯ СХЕМА */
/* Базовая типографика */
.rts-widget-v2-container,
.rts-widget-v2-container * {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
}

.rts-widget-v2-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 356px;
  color: #20323B;
  z-index: 999999;
  margin-top: 28px;
  transform: scale(0.8);
  transform-origin: top left;
}

.rts-widget-v2-container.rts-widget-floating {
  position: fixed;
  right: 24px;
  bottom: 24px;
  margin-top: 0;
}

.rts-widget-v2 {
  position: relative;
  padding: 24px;
  border-radius: 28px;
  background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 0%, rgba(232, 245, 244, 0.9) 55%, rgba(220, 240, 238, 0.88) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  box-shadow: 0 32px 60px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.25);
  overflow: visible;
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}

.rts-widget-v2::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border-radius: 28px;
  padding: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 0%, rgba(210, 237, 236, 0.32) 100%);
  -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
  mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
  -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
  mask-composite: exclude;
}

.rts-widget-v2[data-state="charged"] {
  box-shadow: 0 42px 88px rgba(34, 134, 112, 0.4);
}

.rts-widget-v2[data-state="processing"] {
  box-shadow: 0 38px 72px rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.4);
}

.rts-widget-shell {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
}

.rts-widget-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: nowrap;
}

.rts-widget-header > .rts-widget-trade-pill {
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.rts-widget-trade-pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 0 16px;
  min-height: 38px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.6);
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82) 0%, rgba(225, 242, 241, 0.76) 100%);
  color: #20323B;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  line-height: 1;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-widget-trade-pill:not(.is-disabled):hover {
  border-color: rgba(146, 196, 197, 0.85);
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 0%, rgba(215, 238, 236, 0.85) 100%);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.rts-widget-trade-pill.is-disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: default;
}

.rts-widget-trade-pill svg {
  opacity: 0.7;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}

.rts-widget-trade-number {
  font-size: inherit;
  font-weight: inherit;
}

.rts-widget-status-slot {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  min-height: 38px;
  flex: 1 1 auto;
  min-width: 160px;
}

.rts-timer {
  display: inline-flex;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #20323B;
  background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(241, 250, 250, 0.92) 0%, rgba(224, 243, 241, 0.85) 100%);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.6);
  box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.2);
}

.rts-widget-timer-placeholder {
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.45);
}

.rts-widget-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 18px;
}

.rts-parameter-card {
  position: relative;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 22px;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92) 0%, rgba(230, 245, 244, 0.88) 48%, rgba(214, 239, 238, 0.82) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(176, 204, 208, 0.56);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.18);
  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  transition: border-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
}

.rts-parameter-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 1px;
  border-radius: 21px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6) 0%, rgba(210, 238, 236, 0) 65%);
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}

.rts-parameter-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(152, 196, 195, 0.75);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 26px 52px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.24);
}

.rts-parameter-card:hover::after {
  opacity: 1;
}

.rts-card-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 12px;
}

.rts-card-caption {
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.55);
}

.rts-card-value {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 4px;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #20323B;
}

.rts-card-unit {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.65);
}

.rts-input-field {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}

.rts-input-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.7);
}

.rts-input-control {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.6);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.12);
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-input-control:focus-within {
  border-color: rgba(140, 194, 195, 0.85);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(178, 210, 207, 0.35);
}

.rts-input-prefix {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.7);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.rts-widget-input {
  flex: 1;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  color: #20323B;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

.rts-widget-input::placeholder {
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.35);
}

.rts-widget-input::-webkit-outer-spin-button,
.rts-widget-input::-webkit-inner-spin-button {
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  margin: 0;
}

.rts-widget-input[type='number'] {
  appearance: textfield;
  -moz-appearance: textfield;
}

.rts-slider-block {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
}

.rts-slider-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 12px;
}

.rts-slider-header .rts-input-label {
  flex: 1;
  margin: 0;
}

.rts-slider-input {
  width: 100%;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.45);
  appearance: none;
  outline: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.rts-slider-input::-webkit-slider-thumb {
  appearance: none;
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ECBB9 0%, #9CADCE 100%);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.28);
  margin-top: -8px;
}

.rts-slider-input::-moz-range-thumb {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #71C3B0 0%, #8FA6C7 100%);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(24, 32, 38, 0.45);
  transform: translateY(-8px);
}

.rts-slider-input::-webkit-slider-runnable-track {
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.rts-slider-input::-moz-range-track {
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: transparent;
}

.rts-slider-indicator {
  align-self: flex-start;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(210, 234, 234, 0.68);
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.5);
  color: #20323B;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.rts-segmented {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
}

.rts-segmented-option {
  flex: 1 1 120px;
  min-width: 120px;
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.78);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-segmented-option:hover {
  border-color: rgba(146, 196, 197, 0.8);
  background: rgba(228, 243, 244, 0.92);
}

.rts-segmented-option.is-active {
  border-color: rgba(126, 174, 186, 0.95);
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(207, 235, 235, 0.95) 0%, rgba(194, 229, 231, 0.9) 100%);
  color: #20323B;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.18);
}


.rts-widget-footer {
  display: grid;
  gap: 18px;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.16);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle:hover {
  border-color: rgba(88, 176, 158, 0.55);
  background: rgba(236, 248, 247, 0.95);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.rts-reserve-toggle input {
  position: absolute;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.rts-reserve-visual {
  position: relative;
  width: 42px;
  height: 24px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(210, 234, 234, 0.65);
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  transition: background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-reserve-visual::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 3px;
  left: 3px;
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.28);
  transition: transform 0.25s ease;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle input:checked + .rts-reserve-visual {
  background: rgba(74, 180, 148, 0.75);
  border-color: rgba(56, 158, 129, 0.75);
}

.rts-reserve-toggle input:checked + .rts-reserve-visual::after {
  transform: translateX(18px);
}

.rts-reserve-copy {
  display: grid;
  gap: 4px;
}

.rts-reserve-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: #20323B;
}

.rts-reserve-caption {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.6);
}

.rts-charge-btn {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: none;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  background: linear-gradient(92deg, #A8E1D3 0%, #79C8B6 50%, #49B29F 100%);
  color: #20323B;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 44px rgba(73, 178, 159, 0.26);
}

.rts-charge-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 28px 48px rgba(73, 178, 159, 0.32);
}

.rts-charge-btn:disabled {
  cursor: not-allowed;
  opacity: 0.75;
}

.rts-admin-area {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

.rts-admin-area.is-open .rts-admin-trigger {
  border-color: rgba(146, 196, 197, 0.8);
  background: rgba(228, 243, 244, 0.95);
  color: #20323B;
}

.rts-admin-trigger {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.7);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-admin-trigger:hover {
  border-color: rgba(146, 196, 197, 0.8);
  background: rgba(228, 243, 244, 0.95);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.rts-admin-trigger svg {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  opacity: 0.75;
}

.rts-admin-panel {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: calc(100% + 10px);
  right: 0;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.22);
  display: grid;
  gap: 10px;
}

.rts-admin-panel[hidden] {
  display: none !important;
}

.rts-admin-btn {
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(228, 243, 244, 0.85);
  color: #20323B;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-admin-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(207, 235, 235, 0.95);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.rts-widget-v2[data-state="processing"] .rts-charge-btn {
  background: linear-gradient(92deg, #F5DFA6 0%, #E8C06F 50%, #D9A441 100%);
  color: #3A331F;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 44px rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.26);
}

.rts-widget-v2[data-state="charged"] .rts-charge-btn {
  background: linear-gradient(92deg, #CDE6E4 0%, #A6CCD0 50%, #83B1BE 100%);
  color: #20323B;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 44px rgba(131, 177, 190, 0.26);
}

@media (max-width: 360px) {
  .rts-widget-header {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-right: 0;
  }

  .rts-header-status {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .rts-widget-body {
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .rts-admin-area {
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .rts-widget-notification {
    top: auto;
    bottom: -24px;
    right: 24px;
    transform: translateY(12px);
  }

  .rts-widget-notification.rts-notification-visible {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

.rts-widget-notification {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  right: calc(100% + 24px);
  transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(-16px);
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 16px 18px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.45);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.22);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 14px;
  max-width: 320px;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 3;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}

.rts-widget-notification.rts-notification-visible {
  opacity: 1;
  pointer-events: auto;
  transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(0);
}

.rts-widget-notification.rts-notification-info {
  border-color: rgba(126, 174, 186, 0.45);
  background: rgba(228, 243, 244, 0.95);
}

.rts-widget-notification.rts-notification-success {
  border-color: rgba(87, 179, 150, 0.45);
  background: rgba(224, 244, 237, 0.95);
}

.rts-widget-notification.rts-notification-error {
  border-color: rgba(162, 120, 190, 0.45);
  background: rgba(244, 236, 248, 0.96);
}

.rts-notification-content {
  display: grid;
  gap: 4px;
}

.rts-notification-title {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.rts-notification-text {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(32, 50, 59, 0.68);
}

.rts-notification-progress {
  align-self: center;
  width: 60px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.35);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.rts-notification-progress::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 100%);
  animation: rtsNotificationProgress 3s linear forwards;
  transform-origin: left;
}

@keyframes rtsNotificationProgress {
  from { transform: scaleX(0); }
  to { transform: scaleX(1); }
}

.rts-status-chip {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 0 16px;
  min-height: 38px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
}

.rts-status-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: currentColor;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px currentColor;
}

.status-not-charged {
  color: #8E77AE;
}

.status-in-progress {
  color: #D9A441;
}

.status-in-progress .rts-status-dot {
  animation: rtsStatusPulse 1s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.status-charged {
  color: #3AA88C;
}

@keyframes rtsStatusPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; }
}


.rts-reserve-toggle {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.16);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle:hover {
  border-color: rgba(88, 176, 158, 0.55);
  background: rgba(236, 248, 247, 0.96);
}

.rts-reserve-toggle .toggle-visual {
  position: relative;
  width: 42px;
  height: 24px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(210, 234, 234, 0.65);
  border: 1px solid rgba(178, 204, 210, 0.55);
  transition: background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle input {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.rts-reserve-toggle .toggle-visual::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 3px;
  left: 3px;
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  border-radius: 9px;
  background: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(24, 58, 64, 0.28);
  transition: transform 0.25s ease;
}

